# AhaDiff

Use AhaDiff after code changes to capture verified lessons, claims, quiz cards,
and scores for the current diff.

- Run `ahadiff learn HEAD~1..HEAD` for the latest commit.
- Run `ahadiff learn --staged` before committing staged work.
- Run `ahadiff review` to revisit due SRS cards.
- Run `ahadiff verify <run_id>` before trusting generated artifacts.

Do not write provider secrets, private audit logs, or local provider endpoints
into committed files.
